She just sent one off. So Jesse grew up
in Arkansas, or Mississippi, or something.

116
00:09:32,214 --> 00:09:35,858
他不知道他有一个兄弟，猫王！
但是有一天，大概1968年或69年...
So he didn't know he had a brother, Elvis.
But one day, like, 1968 or '69...

117
00:09:35,926 --> 00:09:39,373
