"Sure would be nice
to be you for one night."

123
00:09:54,133 --> 00:09:57,394
于是，有一场猫王的音乐会其实是他的兄弟在唱。
So Elvis had this concert
where his brother sang.

124
00:09:57,493 --> 00:10:02,129
