Big mistake, because it was his brother
who started to go to Vegas...

128
00:10:10,771 --> 00:10:14,316
穿衣风格大转变，换成了大领子，白连体服，小坎肩。
and wear them big collars,
the white jumpsuits, and the capes.

129
00:10:14,388 --> 00:10:17,868
