436
00:40:48,355 --> 00:40:50,177
杰夫和贝瑞怎么样呀？
How are Jeff and Beryl?

437
00:40:50,338 --> 00:40:55,039
你知道，老样子，老样子
仍然是一些父母奇怪的小伎俩
You know, same old, same old.
Still stuck in their odd little parental ways.

438
00:40:57,122 --> 00:41:00,417
那你没和凯特先生还有孩子在这儿吗？
So you're not with Mr. Cate and the baby
on this trip?

439
00:41:01,057 --> 00:41:05,082
没啦～很不巧的是我自己在这里
要下个星期才能见到呢。
No. Unfortunately, I'm by myself.
I'll see them next week.

440
00:41:09,088 --> 00:41:10,516
他们都挺好的呗？
Everyone's good?

441
00:41:13,088 --> 00:41:14,975
诶～～～～～～
我想要个小孩儿
Yeah, I want a baby.

442
00:41:16,352 --> 00:41:17,780
也不知道啥时候呢...
At some point.

443
00:41:19,296 --> 00:41:22,329
－请问需要些什么？
－你想要点啥，小凯
- What can I get for you?
- What are you having, Catie?

444
00:41:24,928 --> 00:41:27,829
请问可以给我一杯意式浓缩咖啡吗？
要大一点的杯子哟～
Can I have an espresso, please?
In a large cup?

445
00:41:29,151 --> 00:41:31,932
嗯！那我也来杯内个，谢了，双份儿啊！
Yeah, I'll have an espresso, too, thanks.
A double.

446
00:41:31,999 --> 00:41:34,868
可以再给我一小杯热热的牛奶吗？
能不能加热的呢？
And can I have some hot milk on the side?
And could you heat it?

447
00:41:34,942 --> 00:41:37,527
－嗯，我想可以的
－真谢谢你了呢～～
- I think we can manage that.
- Thank you.

448
00:41:42,270 --> 00:41:45,684
真不好意思啊！来晚了
我知道你时间紧
I'm sorry I'm late.
I know you haven't got a lot of time.

449
00:41:46,973 --> 00:41:50,268
啊～～没有关系的，不用担心这个
我想和你在这多坐一会呢
Don't worry about it.
I just wish I could stay here longer.

450
00:41:50,973 --> 00:41:54,747
你在这儿住？还是，只在这儿做你的什么新闻什么的...？
Do you stay here overnight,
or do you just do your press stuff here?

451
00:41:54,813 --> 00:41:56,154
你的晚宴...
Your junket.

452
00:41:58,173 --> 00:42:01,521
不，我住在这里的。也在这做采访。
No, I stay overnight.
And I do the interviews here, too.

453
00:42:01,628 --> 00:42:03,122
这样更方便一些的
I just think it's easier.

454
00:42:03,229 --> 00:42:05,465
直接就可以在我的套房里做采访。
They do the interviews in my suite upstairs.

455
00:42:05,532 --> 00:42:07,866
现在他们在准备下一场采访...
They're setting up for the next interview...

456
00:42:07,931 --> 00:42:12,087
所以，我觉得我们在这里见面更好一些。
and I just thought maybe it would be nicer
if we met down here.

457
00:42:14,555 --> 00:42:17,238
噢算了...夏儿，你不能在这...
No, thanks, Shell. You're not...

458
00:42:19,547 --> 00:42:20,659
来吧！！！～～～
Go on.

459
00:42:21,211 --> 00:42:23,731
他们不会不让你抽的～
They're not going to stop you smoking.

460
00:42:28,795 --> 00:42:30,899
－整吧，姐～
－哎咿～那谢谢啦～
- There you go, cous'.
- Thanks.

461
00:42:35,866 --> 00:42:38,582
那他们就给你一个套房...
So you mean they give you
this full-on hotel suite...

462
00:42:38,649 --> 00:42:41,266
又工作又睡觉的？
and they also use it for your publicity?

463
00:42:43,353 --> 00:42:45,327
真够省的啊～
Seems kind of cheap.

464
00:42:46,233 --> 00:42:50,029
哇噢～～是一个套房耶～
他们可以隔开单独的房间哦～
Well, it's a suite.
So they just divide up the room.

465
00:42:50,105 --> 00:42:52,046
啊，那为啥不能单独给你一个...
Yeah, but why couldn't
they get you a suite...

466
00:42:52,121 --> 00:42:54,837
然后在弄个工作间儿？
and get another suite to do your press in?

467
00:42:55,224 --> 00:42:57,841
现在做的这个预算不是很高的。
It's pretty low-budget, this thing I did.

468
00:42:58,264 --> 00:42:59,605
对，但是...
Yeah, still.

469
00:43:01,239 --> 00:43:02,799
这太便宜糊弄事儿了吧，大妹子！
It's pretty cheap, man.

470
00:43:05,911 --> 00:43:07,471
请问还需要其他的吗？
Can I get you anything else?

471
00:43:07,544 --> 00:43:09,910
－不需要了，谢谢你，这样很好
－您太客气了
- No, thanks. That's great.
- You're welcome.

472
00:43:15,767 --> 00:43:18,766
来这真够费劲的了...差点进不来...
Kind of weird getting in here.
I almost didn't...

473
00:43:20,758 --> 00:43:23,343
直到知道我是你表妹才让进。
until they found out I was your cousin.

474
00:43:24,854 --> 00:43:28,498
在外边儿有狗仔队什么的...
There're some photographer,
paparazzi guys hanging out front.

475
00:43:29,397 --> 00:43:32,266
我猜他们都为了跟着你，对吗？
I guess they kind of
follow you around, right?

476
00:43:32,917 --> 00:43:36,658
噢～你知道，大概是，因为附近会有所谓的名人
You know, whatever so-called celebrities
are around, I suppose.

477
00:43:37,365 --> 00:43:41,041
天呐！有时候你也真够他妈的费事儿了，对吗？
God, that must be
a real fucking drag sometimes, right?

478
00:43:43,028 --> 00:43:44,718
我的意思是，不像我...
I mean, not like me.

479
00:43:45,492 --> 00:43:46,702
无拘无束
I'm free.

480
00:43:47,156 --> 00:43:49,260
一无所有，但是完全自由自在
Practically broke, but I'm completely free.

481
00:43:49,332 --> 00:43:52,201
没人跟踪我，绝逼没人这样...
No one's stalking me,
that's for fucking sure.

482
00:43:53,620 --> 00:43:55,692
除了他们觉得，我是你的内个时候
Except when they thought I was you.

483
00:43:56,275 --> 00:44:00,235
去高级夜店的时候他们以为我是你，才让进
I got into this club once
because they thought I was you.

484
00:44:01,619 --> 00:44:04,684
后来发现了，直接撵走我...
Then they found out I wasn't
and asked me to leave.

485
00:44:04,787 --> 00:44:06,445
真他妈差劲
Pretty fucking rude.

486
00:44:08,658 --> 00:44:11,723
别误会...
我的意思是，你肯定过的特别好，你啥也不缺...
Don't get me wrong.
I mean, it must be fabulous. You got it all.

487
00:44:11,794 --> 00:44:13,932
你有个好老公，漂亮的孩子...
You got a good husband, beautiful baby.

488
00:44:14,002 --> 00:44:16,969
环游世界，住高档酒店...
Travel all over the world,
stay in fancy hotels.

489
00:44:18,193 --> 00:44:19,501
派对...
Parties...

490
00:44:20,209 --> 00:44:23,504
噢～～怎么说呢“这山望着那山高”吧～
You know what they say,
"The grass is always greener."

491
00:44:23,953 --> 00:44:25,545
那...他...
So, how's...

492
00:44:27,633 --> 00:44:28,680
该死的
Shit.

493
00:44:29,200 --> 00:44:30,214
－...强尼...怎么样？
－谁？
- Johnny.
- Who?

494
00:44:30,289 --> 00:44:32,263
吉米，汤米. 对不起.
Jimmy. Tommy. Sorry.

495
00:44:33,585 --> 00:44:34,861
他还好吗？
How is he?

496
00:44:37,712 --> 00:44:40,013
我俩已经黄两年了。
We broke up almost two years ago.

497
00:44:41,712 --> 00:44:43,816
噢～汤米，对，那个龟孙子
Tommy, yeah. What a dickhead.

498
00:44:45,456 --> 00:44:48,041
现在有新的男朋友，李，还记得吗？
Got a new boyfriend now. Lee. Remember?

499
00:44:49,167 --> 00:44:51,501
他玩乐队的，写信的时候提到过他
He's in a band. Wrote you about him.

500
00:44:51,823 --> 00:44:54,211
他在我生活中非常有份量
He's a pretty huge part of my life.

501
00:44:54,991 --> 00:44:57,194
对不起，夏儿，我觉得你没有。
Sorry, Shell, I don't think you did.

502
00:44:57,263 --> 00:44:59,750
有，我还给你发了一张他妈的CD
Yeah, I even sent you his fucking CD.

503
00:45:00,718 --> 00:45:03,587
你助理可能没给你。
Your assistant
probably didn't give it to you.

504
00:45:05,006 --> 00:45:08,966
但是没事儿，真的没事儿
我的意思是，我知道你太忙了...
It's okay. It's totally cool.
I mean, I know how busy your life is.

505
00:45:09,998 --> 00:45:12,779
－你还记得你发到哪里了吗？
－不
- Do you remember where you sent it?
- No.

506
00:45:13,646 --> 00:45:16,067
我的意思是...你一周在洛杉矶...
I mean, one week you're in LA...

507
00:45:16,173 --> 00:45:18,114
然后又在伦敦，然后在悉尼...
then you're in London,
then you're in Sydney.

508
00:45:18,189 --> 00:45:22,018
我的意思是，你根本就没他妈固定的城市
一天一个地儿
I mean, you're in a different fucking city
every day of the week.

509
00:45:34,348 --> 00:45:37,992
我真的想听一听那个音乐，是什么类型的呢？
I'd love to hear the music.
What does it sound like?

510
00:45:39,723 --> 00:45:41,129
内个是很...
It's really...

511
00:45:42,795 --> 00:45:44,223
很躁...
kind of hard...

512
00:45:44,778 --> 00:45:47,494
很给力...差不多是这类型... 
and it's industrial, kind of throbbing...

513
00:45:50,858 --> 00:45:52,865
我觉得你不了解这种
I don't think you'd get it.

514
00:45:56,106 --> 00:45:58,756
－那他们叫什么呢？
－他们叫Sqürl
- What are they called?
- They're called Sqürl.

515
00:45:59,498 --> 00:46:00,708
松鼠？ （松鼠＝Squirrel）
Squirrel?

516
00:46:00,874 --> 00:46:03,557
不，是Sqürl，你知道，都那么叫...
No, Sqürl. You know, like they say it here.

517
00:46:03,625 --> 00:46:06,658
是S-Q-Ü-R-L, Sqürl
S-Q-U-R-L, with an umlaut
over the "U" Sqürl.

518
00:46:08,041 --> 00:46:11,336
啊～～～Sqürl，对对对
Sqürl. I get it. Right.

519
00:46:11,752 --> 00:46:14,206
那找到你给我的那个CD之前，可以先买一张听吗？
So can I buy the CD
until I find the one you sent?

520
00:46:14,313 --> 00:46:18,916
不，还不行，他们是用一个独立厂牌做的，你知道，所以...
No. Not yet. They recorded it independently,
you know, so...

521
00:46:19,336 --> 00:46:22,631
但是我觉得公司终于要出版了
But I think the record company's
gonna put it out finally.

522
00:46:22,696 --> 00:46:23,873
我觉得。
I think.

523
00:46:28,616 --> 00:46:31,844
我真应该找找那张CD，听一下。
I'm gonna have to find that CD
so I can listen to it.

524
00:46:32,903 --> 00:46:34,812
你找不着的
You're not gonna find it.

525
00:46:34,919 --> 00:46:37,569
夏儿，其实，这不公平
Shell, that isn't fair, actually.

526
00:46:38,086 --> 00:46:40,955
－真的，你真找不着！
－真的吗？
- It's true. You're not gonna find it.
- Really?

527
00:46:42,726 --> 00:46:46,587
我他妈绝对清楚，因为我刚才想起来了...
I fucking know you're not.
'Cause I just remembered...

528
00:46:46,694 --> 00:46:49,825
我根本没有发给你。
I didn't actually send it to you.

529
00:46:49,894 --> 00:46:52,828
我觉得，那时侯，想发给你来着。
I think I just thought
about sending it to you.

530
00:47:08,580 --> 00:47:11,579
噢～差点忘了，这是给你的
Almost forgot. This is for you.

531
00:47:12,676 --> 00:47:14,683
谢谢，这是什么？
Thanks. What is it?

532
00:47:17,732 --> 00:47:21,114
这东西很贵的，要好几百块钱呢。
This is really expensive stuff.
It must have cost hundreds.

533
00:47:25,347 --> 00:47:28,063
酷，谢谢，这个我用得上
Cool, thanks. I could use this stuff.

534
00:47:29,443 --> 00:47:31,963
让我像一个大腕儿，对吗
Make me look like a movie star, right?

535
00:47:35,362 --> 00:47:37,303
－干杯
－干杯，斑斓的小妞
- Cheers.
- Cheers, gorgeous.

536
00:47:43,361 --> 00:47:46,426
真心的，小凯，谢谢你见我
Seriously, Catie, thanks for seeing me.

537
00:47:48,257 --> 00:47:50,144
不，应该谢谢你见我才对。
No, thanks for seeing me.

538
00:47:52,513 --> 00:47:55,196
也谢谢你送我昂贵的二手闲置见面礼
And thanks for all the fancy swag.

539
00:47:56,864 --> 00:47:58,270
这不算什么的
It's nothing.

540
00:48:00,512 --> 00:48:02,235
这是闲置对吗？
It is swag, isn't it?

541
00:48:04,160 --> 00:48:06,548
他们肯定送你很多这种东西：
They probably give you
all kinds of free stuff:

542
00:48:06,624 --> 00:48:08,282
珠宝，服饰...
Jewelry, clothes.

543
00:48:08,927 --> 00:48:11,065
有可能还送你汽车，对吗？
Probably give you cars, right?

544
00:48:11,327 --> 00:48:13,944
没，还真没人送车。
No, they don't give me cars.

545
00:48:14,943 --> 00:48:17,626
有时候他们会送我一些化妆品什么的...
They sometimes give me makeup,
from time to time.

546
00:48:17,695 --> 00:48:19,734
但是，我只是觉得...
But I just thought...

547
00:48:19,807 --> 00:48:22,141
我不知道怎么说...我只是想...
I don't know, I just wanted...

548
00:48:22,239 --> 00:48:24,475
我没有时间去购物
Didn't have time to go shopping.

549
00:48:24,766 --> 00:48:28,061
噢噢～没事！这很好
我的意思是，这很不错，我能用...
No, really, it's fine.
I mean, it's great. I can use it.

550
00:48:28,254 --> 00:48:30,937
只是，你不认为这有点儿可笑吗？
It's just funny, don't you think?

551
00:48:31,005 --> 00:48:35,379
你负担不起的东西，对你来说还要花钱是非常渴望不可及
When you can't afford something,
it's really expensive.

552
00:48:35,453 --> 00:48:38,234
但是，你要是负担得起，你都不用自掏腰包，相当于免费！
And then when you can afford it, it's free.

553
00:48:40,445 --> 00:48:42,713
有点颠倒了，你不觉得吗？
Kind of backward, don't you think?

554
00:48:44,861 --> 00:48:48,156
这个世界是有点倾斜的，我猜，在哪儿都是...
The world's a bit like that, I guess,
in a lot of ways.

555
00:48:49,564 --> 00:48:51,451
关于狗仔队...
Speaking of paparazzi...

556
00:48:51,612 --> 00:48:54,426
昨天，我在小报儿上看到你的照片儿
I saw these photos of you the other day
in the tabloids.

557
00:48:54,491 --> 00:48:56,727
啊～不要说那个了，咿呀～～～
Don't tell me that. Yuck.

558
00:48:57,787 --> 00:48:59,445
我穿的什么衣服？
What was I wearing?

559
00:48:59,963 --> 00:49:01,010
对不起.
Sorry.

560
00:49:02,875 --> 00:49:05,525
喂～嗨～琳兹
Hello? Hi, Lindsey.

561
00:49:08,091 --> 00:49:11,571
我和我表妹小夏在楼下的咖啡厅
I'm downstairs, in the coffee room
with my cousin Shelly.

562
00:49:12,634 --> 00:49:14,160
已经要...
It's already...

563
00:49:15,450 --> 00:49:19,377
好吧，好，我这就上去，拜～
Okay, yeah. I'll be up in a minute. Bye.

564
00:49:19,449 --> 00:49:21,041
－你要回去上班儿？
－对啊
- Got to get back to work?
- Yeah.

565
00:49:21,113 --> 00:49:22,705
继续那份苦差事？
Back to the grind?

566
00:49:25,146 --> 00:49:26,607
你想和我一起上去吗？
Do you want to come up to the room?

567
00:49:26,714 --> 00:49:29,812
不是很有意思，但是欢迎你上去
It won't be very interesting,
but you're welcome to come up.

568
00:49:29,881 --> 00:49:32,782
啥？看你做电视采访？？？
What, and watch you do TV interviews
and stuff?

569
00:49:33,049 --> 00:49:35,056
娱乐今宵这种？
Like Entertainment Tonight?

570
00:49:44,344 --> 00:49:48,053
也许，你可以给我那张CD或者给我写信之类的...
Maybe you can send me that CD,
or a letter, or something.

571
00:49:48,151 --> 00:49:52,558
－对，但是，发给你你也看不到
－噢行了，你要是真的发给我我一定会看
- Yeah, but you wouldn't read it.
- Stop it. I would if you actually sent it.

572
00:49:56,151 --> 00:49:58,255
我得要走了，对不起了呢
I've really gotta go. Sorry.

573
00:49:59,670 --> 00:50:02,353
很高兴见到你，你有我的电话号码吗？
It was great seeing you.
Have you got my numbers?

574
00:50:07,478 --> 00:50:10,030
保重了～给大家带好～
Take care. Send my love to everyone.

575
00:50:13,269 --> 00:50:15,985
好，你也帮我带好
Yeah, send my love to everyone
on your end.

576
00:50:20,565 --> 00:50:22,474
...如果他们记得我
If they even remember me.

577
00:50:22,581 --> 00:50:24,588
－拜～小凯
－回见了，夏儿
- Bye, Catie.
- See you, Shell.

578
00:50:25,684 --> 00:50:28,651
这些算在我房间，如果她还要其他的也是。
Put that on my room
and anything else she wants.

579
00:50:28,757 --> 00:50:31,604
－希望下次我可以见到鲁
－啊对
- Maybe next time I'll get to meet Lou.
- Yeah.

580
00:50:32,916 --> 00:50:34,126
是李！
It's Lee.

581
00:50:42,036 --> 00:50:43,312
诶～服务员儿～
Excuse me.

582
00:50:45,427 --> 00:50:48,296
能不能给我来个特基拉，谢了，双份儿的，还要菜单
Can I have a tequila?
Thanks, a double, and the menu.

583
00:50:48,370 --> 00:50:51,184
不好意思小姐，大厅不可以吸烟。
I'm sorry, there's no smoking in the lounge.

584
00:51:11,000 --> 00:51:15,000
杰克为梅格展示他的特斯拉线圈

