- Spoilsport.

743
01:05:06,255 --> 01:05:08,229
－不，这个不行
－对不起
- No, don't do that.
- Sorry.

744
01:05:08,302 --> 01:05:11,236
－我包里可能有
－好吧
- I probably have something in my bag. 
- Okay.

745
01:05:11,631 --> 01:05:13,638
给我一秒钟
Just give me a second here.

746
01:05:14,863 --> 01:05:16,073
噢～老天爷
Oh, gosh.

747
01:05:16,494 --> 01:05:18,435
－非常抱歉
－没关系
- I'm so sorry.
- That's all right.

748
01:05:19,725 --> 01:05:22,310
－给我一点时间
－慢慢来
- Give me one more minute.
- Take your time.

749
01:05:22,382 --> 01:05:26,243
－请签在这里
－好的，你的名字是？
- Here, please, in there.
- Okay, and what's your name?

750
01:05:26,445 --> 01:05:27,492
凯蒂
Katy.

751
01:05:28,365 --> 01:05:30,339
－还有个“Y”
－好的
- With a "Y."
- All right.

752
01:05:31,021 --> 01:05:32,613
“那以后凯蒂做什么”
What Katy did next.

753
01:05:33,293 --> 01:05:35,878
－你好
－阿尔弗雷德也是一个艺人
- Hello.
- Alfred's an actor, too.

754
01:05:38,605 --> 01:05:40,743
－给你
－谢谢你，太棒了
- Here.
- Thank you. Great.

755
01:05:42,636 --> 01:05:45,123
－非常感谢你
－别客气
- Thank you very much.
- You're welcome.

756
01:05:51,084 --> 01:05:53,418
－哇噢～～
－我们继续回到这个
- Wow.
- Let's get back to this.

757
01:05:53,483 --> 01:05:56,450
我不想占用你太多的时间，我知道你很忙
I don't want to take up too much
of your time. I know you're busy.

758
01:05:56,555 --> 01:05:59,402
我说到，我做关于血统族谱的...
As I said, I did this genealogical research...

759
01:05:59,499 --> 01:06:03,208
我只要继续做我爱好的事，我没找什么特别的...
I was just doing it for my own interest.
I wasn't looking for anything specific.

760
01:06:03,274 --> 01:06:05,161
我只是偶然发现这一点...
I just came across this.

761
01:06:05,962 --> 01:06:08,995
我不要在废话连篇了...
I'll cut a long story short.

762
01:06:09,385 --> 01:06:10,562
史蒂夫·库根
Steve Coogan.

763
01:06:11,594 --> 01:06:13,120
噔噔 噔噔～～～～～～～～
Drum roll.

764
01:06:15,113 --> 01:06:16,901
这意味着，史蒂夫...
The thing is, Steve...

765
01:06:17,801 --> 01:06:20,451
你和我是...表亲！！！！
you and I are cousins.

766
01:06:24,233 --> 01:06:27,080
你的意思是？是在艺术上是？
How do you mean? You mean artistically?

767
01:06:27,401 --> 01:06:32,070
不不，我的意思是，这是最通常的解释...
我们是表亲戚，我们是有关系的...
No, I mean in the normal way.
We're cousins. We're related.

768
01:06:35,528 --> 01:06:38,309
－这太令人惊讶了，是不是？
－对，你确定吗？
- It's amazing, isn't it?
- Yeah. Are you sure?

769
01:06:38,376 --> 01:06:40,612
就是这样，你看：
The way it works out is, look:

770
01:06:40,967 --> 01:06:43,388
我爷爷的爷爷...
My great-great grandfather...

771
01:06:44,231 --> 01:06:46,238
是你爷爷的叔叔
is your great-great uncle.

772
01:06:46,311 --> 01:06:51,198
之前，我们的爷爷的爷爷的爸爸，就是一个人。
And further back, we shared
the same great-great-great grandfather.

773
01:06:53,606 --> 01:06:56,507
我的祖先是爱尔兰，但是我知道应该有一个意大利人...
My ancestry is Irish,
but I knew there was an Italian...

774
01:06:56,582 --> 01:06:58,883
对对，就是。就是因为那个意大利人亲戚是...
That's it. The Italian connection is...

775
01:06:58,950 --> 01:07:02,015
爷爷的爷爷的爷爷，他叫朱塞佩
the great-great-great-great grandfather,
Giuseppe.

776
01:07:02,502 --> 01:07:04,989
－这很令人震惊，对吗？
－对，这是...
- Isn't that amazing?
- Yeah, this is...

777
01:07:05,190 --> 01:07:06,848
这是很详细的
This is a lot of detail.

778
01:07:06,918 --> 01:07:10,114
－对，这正是我喜欢的，我只是做一点...
－太令人惊讶了
- It's my thing, I kind of do a little...
- Amazing.

779
01:07:10,181 --> 01:07:14,403
我觉得这太棒了，我可以说史蒂夫·库根是我的亲人！ 
I think it's just great to be able to say
that I'm related to Steve Coogan.

780
01:07:14,469 --> 01:07:18,363
我也是，我可以告诉别人我和阿尔伯特·莫里纳沾亲戚 
Likewise, I can tell people
I'm related to Albert Molina.

781
01:07:18,437 --> 01:07:19,582
阿尔弗雷德！
Alfred.

782
01:07:22,884 --> 01:07:26,047
这是我奶奶，她在家谱里份量可不轻...
It's my grandmother who's the big one
on the family tree.

783
01:07:26,116 --> 01:07:27,490
她一定非常的兴奋！
She'll be very thrilled.

784
01:07:27,555 --> 01:07:30,871
她也是你庞大的粉丝儿，她喜欢你在...
She's a huge fan of your work.
She loved you in...

785
01:07:33,923 --> 01:07:35,133
《不羁夜》的表演。
Boogie Nights.

786
01:07:35,235 --> 01:07:37,623
真的？那个在里面穿裤衩举枪的那个？
Right. With the shorts and the shotgun?

787
01:07:37,731 --> 01:07:40,032
对，她提起过一次关于那个电影
Yeah, she talked about that once.

788
01:07:40,547 --> 01:07:41,855
太好了
Great.

789
01:07:41,954 --> 01:07:45,848
我知道这是很突然的，但是你想想我们是表亲的可能性有多大？
I know this is coming right out of the blue,
but just think of the possibilities.

790
01:07:45,923 --> 01:07:48,191
这太神奇了不是吗？你看...
It's fantastic. Let's look at the facts.

791
01:07:48,258 --> 01:07:52,480
我们都是艺人，我们是表亲，我们已经证明了这一切
We're both actors.
We're cousins, we've established that.

792
01:07:53,442 --> 01:07:56,507
也许我们可以一起工作，比如演戏...
We could maybe work together,
do a play maybe.

793
01:07:56,578 --> 01:07:58,617
或许我们一起拍个电影...
We could make a movie.

794
01:07:58,689 --> 01:08:01,274
我们可以拍一个，关于这个故事...
We could actually do a movie
about this story.

795
01:08:01,345 --> 01:08:04,661
关于发现，我们这了不起的关系，我们是表兄弟啊～～～
About discovering this amazing thing
between us, that we're cousins.

796
01:08:04,769 --> 01:08:06,656
比如，这故事要两个演员...
The story could be two actors...

797
01:08:06,721 --> 01:08:10,517
他们发现他们竟然是表亲，那我们可以自导自演啊...
who discover that they're cousins.
We can actually play ourselves.

798
01:08:10,625 --> 01:08:14,236
我们在电影里，我是弗雷德·莫里纳，你是史蒂夫...
We'd be in the movie.
I'd be Fred Molina, you'd be Steve...

799
01:08:14,304 --> 01:08:16,725
我们在电影里是表亲！！！！
We'd be cousins in the movie.

800
01:08:17,728 --> 01:08:21,023
这实在太棒了！实在太美妙了～
It's fantastic. It'd be great, absolutely great.

801
01:08:22,687 --> 01:08:26,810
你知道，也许不拍，我们可以一起出街...
You know, or not. We could just hang out.

802
01:08:26,943 --> 01:08:30,074
我们或许有时候一起喝个啤酒什么的，还不错
We should definitely go
for a beer sometime. That'd be great.

803
01:08:30,142 --> 01:08:33,916
也许，我们一起去旅游，我们两个人...
Maybe go on vacation together,
just the two of us...

804
01:08:34,494 --> 01:08:36,632
可以更加相互了解...
sort of get to know each other.

805
01:08:42,717 --> 01:08:44,539
你不是同志是吗？你不是
You're not gay are you?

806
01:08:45,149 --> 01:08:46,130
不是
No.

807
01:08:46,685 --> 01:08:48,245
不，我已经结婚了
No, I'm married.

808
01:08:48,509 --> 01:08:50,264
詹姆斯一世也是这样
So was James I.

809
01:08:51,133 --> 01:08:54,394
对不起，我不知道，这是我突然感觉到的
Sorry. I don't know,
that just popped into my head.

810
01:08:54,461 --> 01:08:57,330
－随口一问，为了避免尴尬
－嗯，我明白
- Say it, get it out of the way.
- I understand.

811
01:08:57,821 --> 01:08:59,315
我明白你是怎么想的...
I know exactly what you're thinking.

812
01:08:59,389 --> 01:09:01,657
如果有一天突然来个人对我说“我是你的表亲”...
If somebody came up to me going,
"I'm your cousin"...

813
01:09:01,724 --> 01:09:03,828
我也觉得这人脑子不好...
I'd think they were a nutter as well.

814
01:09:03,900 --> 01:09:05,394
认真的讲，我真的没有疯...
Take it from me, I'm not crazy.

815
01:09:05,468 --> 01:09:09,722
我只觉得这是好的出奇的......
I just think
this is a fantastic, extraordinary...

816
01:09:10,332 --> 01:09:12,720
－对我来说是非常愉快的
－当然
- delightful thing for me.
- Absolutely.

817
01:09:12,828 --> 01:09:15,445
－我只是想让你知道这些...
－嗯嗯嗯
- And I just wanted you to know about it.
- Ditto.

818
01:09:15,803 --> 01:09:18,039
我只要，如果我想要什么...
All I want, if I want anything...

819
01:09:18,107 --> 01:09:22,579
只要你承认这好的出奇的关系...
is for you to just acknowledge
this extraordinary thing...

820
01:09:25,082 --> 01:09:27,121
和爱我
and just love me.

821
01:09:35,129 --> 01:09:37,136
嗯哼～可以
Yeah, I could do that.

822
01:09:48,473 --> 01:09:51,953
我得走了
I have to go.

823
01:09:53,208 --> 01:09:56,077
还没告诉你，我还有个见面会
I didn't tell you. I have this meeting.

824
01:09:56,248 --> 01:09:58,255
－其实时间已经调前了
－啊～～
- It actually moved forward.
- I see.

825
01:09:58,328 --> 01:10:02,418
是在环球，会计和投资商这类...
It's at Universal.
Number crunchers, financiers...

826
01:10:09,911 --> 01:10:11,437
－这...
－这是给你的
- This...
- That's for you.

827
01:10:11,542 --> 01:10:13,451
－噢～不错
－是你的
- That's great.
- It's yours.

828
01:10:15,542 --> 01:10:19,153
－我会放到我的资料柜里
－当然
- I'll make sure that gets filed.
- Sure.

829
01:10:20,182 --> 01:10:22,123
你还要在这几天，对吗？
You'll be here a couple of days, right?

830
01:10:22,197 --> 01:10:24,782
也许你临走前我们可以再见一面...
So maybe we could see each other
before you go.

831
01:10:25,878 --> 01:10:28,212
只要确认一下我的日程...
Just checking the mental diary...

832
01:10:33,557 --> 01:10:37,353
情况不太好，在这里的时间...
This is not good, the time I'm here.

833
01:10:37,556 --> 01:10:39,628
－已经满满当当的了
－我明白我明白
- It's just that it's packed.
- I understand.

834
01:10:39,700 --> 01:10:40,714
没问题
No problem.

835
01:10:40,788 --> 01:10:44,497
给我你的手机号儿走之前我给你打电话
Give me your cell phone number,
and I'll call you before you go.

836
01:10:44,564 --> 01:10:46,254
这有个插曲...
There's a story there.

837
01:10:46,708 --> 01:10:49,358
在美国的运营商的信号...
There's a tri-band system
here in the States...

838
01:10:49,427 --> 01:10:52,274
和英国的不一样...
which is different to the system in the UK...

839
01:10:52,371 --> 01:10:54,159
是一种...
and it's a kind of...

840
01:10:54,611 --> 01:10:58,505
我们的手机拿到这里用不了，所以，我是没有手机的...
The cell phones, they don't work here.
So I'm kind of cell phone-less...

841
01:10:58,579 --> 01:11:00,651
－在美国
－我了解
- in the US.
- I see.

842
01:11:01,714 --> 01:11:04,234
那给我你的座机号码也行，我给你打
Well, give me your home number.
I'll call you.

843
01:11:04,307 --> 01:11:06,379
－你有我助理的号码不是么？
－对
- You've got my PA's number, right?
- Yeah.

844
01:11:06,451 --> 01:11:08,523
很好，我们可以这样联络
Great, then we're connected.

845
01:11:08,786 --> 01:11:11,403
你不能给我你家的电话号码吗？
Can't you give me your number at home?

846
01:11:14,098 --> 01:11:15,526
我能说不吗？
Can I say no?

847
01:11:15,986 --> 01:11:20,622
因为，这不是针对你的...
Because nothing,
absolutely nothing personal...

848
01:11:20,689 --> 01:11:25,358
只是我从来没给别人我的号码，从未...
It's just that I never
give my number out, ever.

849
01:11:25,425 --> 01:11:27,366
这是我的隐私...
It's just a personal space thing.

850
01:11:27,441 --> 01:11:31,499
这是一个规则...我常对自己说“坚持规则”
It's just a rule and I always think,
"Stick to the rule."

851
01:11:32,240 --> 01:11:34,825
其实更好称之为理论而不是规则...
It's more of a philosophy than a rule.

852
01:11:37,872 --> 01:11:41,646
有很多名人我都没有给...
I've not given my number out
to many eminent people in the past.

853
01:11:41,712 --> 01:11:44,013
