So you're in good company.

855
01:11:48,463 --> 01:11:51,975
如果山姆·曼德斯都觉得好的话
对我也是
If it's good enough for Sam Mendes,
it's good enough for me.

856
01:11:57,294 --> 01:12:00,195
－我觉得是我的
－对对对，我的不能用
- I think it's me.
- Right, because mine doesn't work.

857
01:12:00,270 --> 01:12:02,887
失陪，我得接个电话...很快回来
I'm sorry, I got to take this. I'll get back.

858
01:12:03,694 --> 01:12:04,642
你好？
Hello?

859
01:12:06,029 --> 01:12:07,435
是，当然
Yeah, sure.

860
01:12:09,646 --> 01:12:12,842
