Spike, hi. How you doing?

861
01:12:13,229 --> 01:12:15,017
你收到信息了
You got the message.

862
01:12:15,085 --> 01:12:19,175
我经纪人给你打电话确认过我们说的是一样
My agent just called you just to make sure
we're all on the same page.

863
01:12:19,980 --> 01:12:24,583
不，我们都是制片人，因为这样可以确保无误
No, the producer credit is just so you and I
can sort of keep tabs on everything.

864
01:12:24,652 --> 01:12:26,855
