You know, artistic integrity,
that sort of thing.

865
01:12:26,924 --> 01:12:29,771
要不然的话，很可能功亏一篑
Otherwise the whole thing
could just run away.

866
01:12:32,588 --> 01:12:34,562
你啊你！不
You bastard, no.

867
01:12:35,627 --> 01:12:36,674
好吧
All right.

868
01:12:36,747 --> 01:12:39,430
那还是周日？好，好的
You still okay for Sunday? Good. All right.

869
01:12:39,499 --> 01:12:42,346
我在那儿见你吗？
好，好，尽早
Will I meet you there?
All right. Nice and early.

870
01:12:42,411 --> 01:12:45,574
好的，对，哥们儿，拜，斯派克
Okay, yeah. Lots of love. Bye, Spike.

871
01:12:47,018 --> 01:12:49,472
－很抱歉
－噢，没事儿
- I'm sorry about that.
- It's okay, fine.

872
01:12:52,874 --> 01:12:54,913
是斯派克·李吗？
Was that Spike Lee?

873
01:12:55,018 --> 01:12:59,011
不，我不认识斯派克·李
是斯派克·琼斯
No. I don't even know Spike Lee.
That was Spike Jonze.

874
01:13:00,778 --> 01:13:03,494
－我很崇拜他
－对，他是个好人
- I love him.
- Yeah, he's a good man.

875
01:13:04,041 --> 01:13:07,172
我们是老朋友
We've been friends for a long time now.

876
01:13:07,401 --> 01:13:09,505
我们都喜欢户外远足
We're both keen hikers.

877
01:13:09,929 --> 01:13:12,612
－这没什么可说的
－不，继续
- Well, it's very boring.
- No, go on.

878
01:13:13,064 --> 01:13:17,057
我们在同一个户外俱乐部，周末常去远足
We belong to a club,
and we go hiking at weekends.

879
01:13:17,448 --> 01:13:21,408
他是一个非常坚定的环保主义者
He's a very committed environmentalist.

880
01:13:21,672 --> 01:13:25,566
斯派克·琼斯是个环境保护狂
天呐，之前真不知道他这么缺...
Spike Jonze is a tree-hugger.
Jesus, I never had him down as that.

881
01:13:29,319 --> 01:13:32,352
我认为，或许他更喜欢你称他为“叶人”
I think he prefers the term "leaf people"...

882
01:13:33,159 --> 01:13:34,533
我也是
as do I.

883
01:13:37,734 --> 01:13:41,628
嗯，我的意思是，这个...
别误会，这很好
Right, I mean, that's...
Don't get me wrong. That's great.

884
01:13:42,694 --> 01:13:46,687
我喜爱树，我觉得应该有更多的树
I love trees.
I think there should be more of them.

885
01:13:47,877 --> 01:13:50,298
用纸的时候两面都用
When I use paper, I use both sides.

886
01:13:51,845 --> 01:13:53,503
我很乐意...
I would love to...

887
01:13:58,853 --> 01:14:01,470
你知道，我要撤销那个...
You know, I'm going to tear up...

888
01:14:01,541 --> 01:14:04,769
关于电话号码的那个白痴规则
that stupid rule about phone numbers.

889
01:14:05,668 --> 01:14:07,260
太他妈缺了
It's such shit.

890
01:14:09,412 --> 01:14:12,543
如果现在再给你我的电话号码，你是不是觉得我很差劲？
Would it be shabby of me
to give you my number now?

891
01:14:15,556 --> 01:14:16,504
是
Yeah.

892
01:14:26,115 --> 01:14:28,602
