01:25:05,488 --> 01:25:08,619
导体...
of acoustical resonance.

1040
01:25:12,047 --> 01:25:14,730
我真的不明白你想说什么
I have no idea what you're talking about.

1041
01:25:16,975 --> 01:25:18,884
你能解释一下吗？
Can you explain it to me?

1042
01:25:19,087 --> 01:25:21,639
－不，不行
－好吧
- No, not really.
- I know.

1043
01:25:22,703 --> 01:25:25,037
让我们以咖啡代香槟...
Let's pretend this coffee is champagne.

1044
01:25:26,926 --> 01:25:28,681
为什么要这样？
Why would we do that?

1045
01:25:29,326 --> 01:25:31,398
哇噢～让我们感受赞扬生命
Well, to celebrate life.

1046
01:25:32,910 --> 01:25:36,041
你知道，像有钱有品味的人...
You know, like the rich, elegant people do.

1047
01:25:37,038 --> 01:25:38,761
那些豪绅们...
The classy people.

1048
01:25:40,205 --> 01:25:44,066
我比较喜欢咖啡，简单的，亲民的咖啡...
I prefer coffee.
Simple, working man's coffee.

1049
01:25:46,701 --> 01:25:50,726
你真是个土老冒，比尔
你知道你的问题是什么吗？
You're so provincial, Bill.
Do you know what your problem is?

1050
01:25:52,236 --> 01:25:53,250
是什么？
What?

1051
01:25:55,020 --> 01:25:58,664
你没有生活乐趣
You have no joie de vivre.

1052
01:26:00,811 --> 01:26:01,988
当真？
I don't?

1053
01:26:03,659 --> 01:26:07,073
真的，而且，这个咖啡很烂
No. Besides, this coffee is awful.

1054
01:26:09,579 --> 01:26:12,993
－对，真的不好，是不是？
－糟透了
- You're right. It really is bad, isn't it?
- Dreadful.

1055
01:26:14,219 --> 01:26:16,193
让我们举杯～
I propose a toast.

1056
01:26:17,515 --> 01:26:19,402
为了什么举杯？
So what should we toast?

1057
01:26:22,506 --> 01:26:25,637
为了20年代的巴黎！
Paris in the 1920s.

1058
01:26:25,961 --> 01:26:28,677
约瑟芬·贝克，红磨坊
Josephine Baker, the Moulin Rouge.

1059
01:26:29,321 --> 01:26:31,360
“怎么样，好吗？”
"What is it? Okay?"

1060
01:26:32,905 --> 01:26:34,213
也为...
And also...

1061
01:26:34,952 --> 01:26:37,472
70年代的纽约...
New York in the '70s.

1062
01:26:37,769 --> 01:26:39,678
70年代晚期...
In the late '70s.

1063
01:26:40,553 --> 01:26:42,375
真的？好吧
Really? All right.

1064
01:26:42,985 --> 01:26:44,740
干杯
Cheers.

1065
01:26:50,119 --> 01:26:51,777
味道好极了，是不是？
Delicious, isn't it?

1066
01:26:53,767 --> 01:26:57,115
香槟酒：来自神的甘露
Champagne: Nectar of the gods.

1067
01:26:58,727 --> 01:27:01,858
这就是你的午饭？咖啡和一根烟？
Is that all you're having for lunch,
coffee and a cigarette?

1068
01:27:01,927 --> 01:27:03,617
这不太健康
It's not very healthy.

1069
01:27:05,255 --> 01:27:06,978
我们已经吃了午饭
We had lunch earlier.

1070
01:27:10,278 --> 01:27:11,455
吃了吗？
We did?

1071
01:27:12,997 --> 01:27:17,022
我们现在在休息，喝咖啡
We're on a break here, a coffee break.

1072
01:27:18,629 --> 01:27:20,352
多压抑啊～
How depressing.

1073
01:27:21,669 --> 01:27:23,676
我们要休息多久？
How long is our break, anyway?

1074
01:27:23,781 --> 01:27:27,009
10分钟左右，但是快结束了
About 10 minutes, and it's nearly over now.

1075
01:27:30,981 --> 01:27:32,671
告诉我这不是真的
Say it isn't true.

1076
01:27:35,300 --> 01:27:37,209
－啊？
－什么？
- Well?
- What?

1077
01:27:38,372 --> 01:27:41,088
我说你要告诉我这不是真的
I asked you to say it isn't true.

1078
01:27:41,668 --> 01:27:43,326
说什么不是真的？
Say what isn't true?

1079
01:27:45,251 --> 01:27:46,941
算了！
Never mind.

1080
01:27:48,771 --> 01:27:50,875
那我要打个盹儿
Anyway, I have to have a nap.

1081
01:27:53,283 --> 01:27:56,697
那休息结束时你叫我
So call me when the break is over.

1082
01:27:59,330 --> 01:28:03,737
那，你还有不到两分钟的盹儿
Well, you have two minutes or less
for your nap.

1083
01:28:43,039 --> 01:28:44,926
现在，新闻！
And now, the news.

